- The Software Roadmap 🗺️
To stay organized and avoid "configuration drift" (where one worker is different from the other), let's tackle the setup in this specific order:

    The Database (VM4): We’ll install MySQL and set up the schema first so the workers have something to connect to immediately. 🗄️

    The Workers (VM2 & VM3): We’ll install Node.js and Nginx, then deploy your code. 💻

    The Load Balancer (VM1): Finally, we’ll configure Nginx to sit in front of the workers. ⚖️




